7.1,, 89,, Biography, Drama,, Xaver Schwarzenberger,, Heike Makatsch, Felix Eitner, Hary Prinz, Donald Arthur,, Based on the life of German toymaker Margarete Steiff, the movie shows her long way from a 10-year-old girl, confined to a wheelchair, to one of the first and most successful creators of toy stuffed animals.